text: Guillaume Thevenot (born September 13, 1993 in La Garenne-Colombes) is a French cyclist riding for the CC Nogent-sur-Oise amateur team in France. ==Major results== ;2011 : 2nd Chrono des Nations Juniors ;2013 : 3rd National Under-23 Road Race Championships : 7th Polynormande ;2014 : 1st Stage 4 (TTT) Ronde de l'Isard : 3rd National Under-23 Road Race Championships ==References== ==External links== * * Category:People from La Garenne-Colombes Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Hauts-de-Seine
title: Guillaume Thévenot
